    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It starts and runs reliably and is suitable for regular daily use. The exterior shows minor cosmetic wear such as small scratches or light scuffs, and the interior has some visible use but remains functional and intact. No major mechanical issues are present, though routine maintenance should be expected.",
